title: Destination Truth Complete 1st Season DivX
description: Destination Truth is a weekly SciFi Original Series that premiered on June 6, 2007. The series follows paranormal investigator Joshua Gates around the world to investigate claims of the supernatural, mainly in the field of cryptozoology. The first season of the show was created and produced by Mandt Bros. Productions.
